00˚C until required.","The slightly tart gooseberry has a relatively short season in the UK, from June-July, but you can always freeze them if you want to use them at a different time. Use this curd in the gooseberry layer cake, also delicious made into a gooseberry fool, or spread on toast or buns."],"basicInfo":["easy","15m","1h","1 total recipe"]}